<p>
  As a participant in the auction, you have 500 tickets, to use
  between the raffle and live auction.
</p>

<p>
  <b><a href="/items">Raffle:</a></b><br/>
  <b>To view the items in the raffle,</b>select the
  <a href="/items">items tab</a> at the top of
  the page. There, you can see each item, the itemâ€™s host/contributor,
  how many of each item are in the raffle, and how many  tickets are in
